{"tid":2411174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場：黃學禮阻差辦公案　司法機構首以保護為證人的警員為由    限記者聽審","createTime":"2021-02-17T06:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T07:37:04.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d4f44056c5b4090905d18e2e9693e827ede092","tid":2411174,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:58:02.000Z","msg":"前年 8 月 7 日凌晨有市民包圍深水埗警署，抗議警方拘捕前浸大學生會會長方仲賢，沙田區議員黃學禮在場遭警員制服，事後被控阻差辦公，案件今（17日）在西九龍裁判法院開審。法庭原定安排7名記者入庭，但今早突然禁止部分已取籌的記者入內，包括《蘋果日報》及《立場新聞》記者。<br />\n<br />\n現場保安聲稱要保護匿名作供警員，指屏風未能完全遮掩其容貌，最終只容許4名記者進入，是法院首次以此為由拒絕記者入庭。其他記者周旋近兩小時後才獲准入內，但當時警員已作供完畢。<br />\n<br />\n稍後有詳細報道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3903614059724185/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3903614059724185%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN26f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=2013f509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3903614059724185/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"e09859a4c8b830a022dcba67c84169b6641dba1d","tid":2411174,"uid":46099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:12:10.000Z","msg":"法庭又唔比影相，又有禁起警員底嘅禁制令，咁做有意思咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d4f7b7ecb3062e8604bbcb9988d8a58a2f5fa4","tid":2411174,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"i can face all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b5511632cded1a8a3803dfa013c1c3bdb19186","tid":2411174,"uid":173060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"做乜咁驚呀， d 狗樣唔見得人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}